Package org.opends.server.replication.server

Class MsgQueue

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.opends.server.replication.server.MsgQueue
  • @ThreadSafe
public class MsgQueue
extends Object
    This class is used to build ordered lists of UpdateMsg. The order is defined by the order of the CSN of the UpdateMsg.

      • consumeUpTo

        public void consumeUpTo​(UpdateMsg finalMsg)
        Consumes all the messages in this queue up to and including the passed in message. If the passed in message is not contained in the current queue, then all messages will be removed from it.
        Parameters:
        finalMsg - the final message to reach when consuming messages from this queue
